                      <h4>Quick Facts</h4>
                      <br style="line-height:12px" />
                      <a name="what">WHAT TXT411 DOES:</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;TXT411 is the delivery mechanism for Super Banner Mobile Coupons, which provide a quick and convenient way for you to receive and save special offers about products or services you've seen in online advertisements. A text message containing information about the offer is sent to your mobile phone from TXT411 (898411) when you request a Super Banner Mobile Coupon online.<br />
                      <br style="line-height:12px" />
                      <a name="how">HOW TO USE TXT411:</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;When you encounter an online advertisement that offers Super Banner Mobile Coupons, you can request a coupon by providing your mobile phone number together with any other required information and clicking the submit button. The special offer information you've requested will be sent as a text message from TXT411 to your mobile phone.<br />
                      <br style="line-height:12px" />
                      <a name="how">MESSAGING COSTS:</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;Standard text message rates apply. Messages will be billed for in accordance with the terms of your contract with your mobile telecom provider.<br />
                      <br style="line-height:12px" />
                      <a name="control">YOU'RE IN CONTROL:</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;You will only receive a text message from TXT411 when you have asked us to send it to you by completing a Super Banner Mobile Coupon request form at an advertiser's web site. Nevertheless, should you decide that you do not want us to send any coupons to your mobile phone in the future, you can opt out of receiving text messages from us.<br />
                      <br style="line-height:12px" />
                      <a name="optout">HOW TO OPT OUT:</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;To opt out of receiving any further text messages from TXT411, submit an <a href="/mobile_phones/new">opt-out request</a> online at this site, or send a text message containing the word STOP to 898411 from your mobile phone. Once we've processed your request, which should take no more than a few seconds, you will no longer receive text messages from TXT411.<br />
                      <br style="line-height:13px" />
                      <a name="help">HOW TO GET HELP:</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;You can text HELP to 898411 at any time to get help sent to your mobile phone. You can also consult our <a href="#faqs">FAQs</a> section online, email our help desk at <a href="mailto:support@txt411.com">support@txt411.com</a>, or call our toll-free support line at (877) 898-4114.<br />
